trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de tempo de design para <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"> </xref>, e <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"> </xref> controles.

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner is a multi-purpose designer that provides design-time rendering for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> controls, which both inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> base class.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner é um designer de multiuso que fornece processamento de tempo de design e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>controles, os dois que herdam da <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>classe de base</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner serves as a standard control designer, adding only what customization is needed to validate the associated control and apply its design mode state to the design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner serve como um designer de controle padrão, adicionando apenas quais personalização é necessária para validar o controle associado e aplicar seu estado de modo de design para o processamento de tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: If you have a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> control, you can create a derived designer, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, to provide design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Se você tiver um personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>controle, você pode criar um designer derivado, como <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, para fornecer processamento em tempo de design.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: You can safely override any of the members as needed; however, when overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to call the base implementation to avoid losing design mode state information.
trans-unit.target: Você pode substituir qualquer um dos membros com segurança conforme o necessário; No entanto, ao substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>método, certifique-se de chamar a implementação base para evitar a perda de informações de estado de modo de design.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma cópia do associado <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> controle processar em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Esse método é substituído para copiar informações de zona para o controle de exibição.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control.

Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se o controle reside em uma zona do tipo <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>e, em seguida, obtém a marcação que é usada para representar o controle em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A marcação que é usada para representar o controle em tempo de design, ou marcação de erro se o controle não reside em um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>-derivado controle associado com o designer.
